    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/bb61a73035e352d478198a3ecf342e87.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>《灵魂原理重启（Soul Axiom Rebooted）》是一款第一人称视角剧情冒险解谜游戏。故事发生在网络世界 Elysia，这里美好而令人难忘。收集独特的手之能力，探索多重结局，决定自己的命运，揭开数码的来世之谜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/6f2a91a8b08b75947cb15308a6d1f886.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>您将踏上引人入胜的探索旅程，途经美丽迷人的场景，面对危险重重的挑战，揭示您的身份、故事和秘密。但是要当心：有些谜团还是不要解开为好。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/a8e6966ae1e003be3898e36625d44fe5.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>解开隐秘的逻辑和动作谜题，发现线索并探索记忆，解锁您身份的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/84c940c82e9967d5736aba7900f30633.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>共有 6 个章节，40 个独特场景，100 多个谜题和 63 个游戏内成就——预计 20 多小时独具魅力的游戏内容。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/d186665aa86a29befe6d5c9d91cc4287.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>发现并收集独特的手之能力，帮助您探索并解开谜题。在我们的动态自适应环境（Dynamic Adaptive Environments)下，运用您的能力操纵周围环境。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/bffaee8f0fa5b8f4241a8b9597977d82.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>游戏搭配紧张而发人深省的旁白，引出多种结局，令您渴望探索传说的其他故事路径。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/d9a47fde647b1021023b94f8d75bbfd0.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>画面风格美丽简约，着重突出醒目的形状、强烈的色彩和令人惊叹的效果，引出 Elysia 中丰富的情感脉络。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/686972189c44fa3eee0f410150ba0468.webp?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206620/extras/3d68e04391c18c1a7ed08c763213621c.avif?t=1638522554\" width=596 height=118 /></span><br><br>50 段原创背景音乐巧妙契合您在记忆中的探索之旅，增强游戏氛围。",
